```

Here is the example with the algorithm information encoded in the outer protected header as {"enc": "A128GCM"}.
So, the value of "A128GCM" would go into the next_layer_alg member of the recipient structure. If you think about the recipients structure as the layer up, then the outer header would be the layer down. That is what we call it in COSE HPKE but if you know a better name then I am happy to use it.

